    "section_accordion_group_cxzrjN": {
      "type": "section-accordion-group",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_jKhp89": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Budding Florist FAQs"
          }
        },
        "question_CpP7CQ": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "default_open": false,
            "title": "I’m just getting started. Is Floral Pricing for the Budding Florist too advanced for me?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely not! We created this digital guide to be what we wish existed when we were starting out in the floral business. The sooner you can apply the formulas we teach, the faster you’ll be growing a profitable business.</p>",
            "show_icon": false,
            "icon_name": "icon-award",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": ""
          }
        },
        "question_FcYyDV": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "default_open": false,
            "title": "I’ve been in business 3+ years already. Is this content still relevant?",
            "content": "<p>You betcha. If you ever find yourself thinking “Have I priced this right?” or “Is this recipe going to work for the budget?” then you’ll find the answers in Floral Pricing for the Budding Florist.</p>",
            "show_icon": false,
            "icon_name": "icon-award",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": ""
          }
        },
        "question_FEYLAH": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "default_open": false,
            "title": "What season are the recipe examples from?",
            "content": "<p>Share details about your shipping policies, item returns, or customer service.Great question! The majority of Floral Pricing for the Budding Florist has been written using flowers that are available year-round from most wholesalers. In the BONUS section we’ve included recipes from a few seasonal designs, just to give you ideas of what can be achieved at different times of year.</p>",
            "show_icon": false,
            "icon_name": "icon-award",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": ""
          }
        },
        "question_PWeCmz": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "default_open": false,
            "title": "What if I use Floral Pricing for the Budding Florist course and still need help?",
            "content": "<p>We’ve got you covered. When you purchase this digital guide you also get the option to purchase additional 1:1 Coaching from Bloom Culture founder, Alison Fleck. Alison has been recipe writing, ordering and designing for 12+ years so if you’ve got a question, she’ll have the answer!</p>",
            "show_icon": false,
            "icon_name": "icon-award",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": ""
          }
        },
        "question_jCYKNx": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "default_open": false,
            "title": "When do I get the guide?",
            "content": "<p>You’ll receive everything as an instant digital download so you can get started right away!</p>",
            "show_icon": false,
            "icon_name": "icon-award",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": ""
          }
        },
        "question_eyj3ML": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "default_open": false,
            "title": "Are refunds availble?",
            "content": "<p>Due to the digital nature of this product, no refunds are available. If you have any questions about whether this product will be beneficial to you and your business, before you purchase, please <a href=\"https://bloomcultureflowers.com/pages/contact\" title=\"https://bloomcultureflowers.com/pages/contact\">contact us.</a></p>",
            "show_icon": false,
            "icon_name": "icon-award",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": ""
          }
        }
      },
